<head>Evidence on the Mountain Meadow Massacre.</head>
  
<dateline><placeName type="settlement" key="Salt Lake City, UT">SALT LAKE CITY</placeName>, Sept, 25.</dateline><p>&#8212;<seg type="Blame" subtype="LDS_LDSLeadership">Affidavits were taken here today regarding the Mountain Meadow massacre, which fully corroborate the testimony of Bishop <persName key="Klingensmith, Philip">Smith</persName>, and give further details
showing more positively the guilt of the Mormon leaders.</seg>  Testimony was obtained here today proving the identity of the assassins of Dr. <persName key="Robinson, J. King">Robinson</persName>.</p>

